|<span data-ttu-id="f9b07-106">Parámetro</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f9b07-106">Parameter</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="f9b07-107">Configura</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f9b07-107">Configures</span></span>|  
|---------------|----------------|  
|<xref:System.Management.Instrumentation.WmiConfigurationAttribute.Scope>|<span data-ttu-id="f9b07-108">El espacio de nombres en el que el proveedor expone las clases.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f9b07-108">The namespace in which your provider exposes classes.</span></span>|  
|<xref:System.Management.Instrumentation.WmiConfigurationAttribute.NamespaceSecurity>|<span data-ttu-id="f9b07-109">-La seguridad (DACL) en el espacio de nombres utilizado.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f9b07-109">-   The security (DACL) on the namespace used.</span></span>|  
|<xref:System.Management.Instrumentation.WmiConfigurationAttribute.HostingModel>|<span data-ttu-id="f9b07-110">-El modelo de hospedaje que se usará el proveedor.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f9b07-110">-   The hosting model that will be used by the provider.</span></span>|  
